          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/karaglade/" class=" " title="斗篷客">斗篷客</a>
                (一日难再晨。)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31483337">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31483337/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p31483337-2.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-05 11:51</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p31483337-2.jpg" alt="然道与世事不并兴，若不废人间之务，何得修如此之志乎？"><br><span class="pic-title">然道与世事不并兴，若不废人间之务，何得修如此之志乎？</span></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

